<p><strong><a href="http://scpper.com/page/789889960">scpper上的作者</a> <span style="color: grey">|</span> <a href="http://scpexplained.wikidot.com/apas">解释</a></strong></p>
</div>
<hr />
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4665703); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4665703&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609579771" alt="Nagiros" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4665703)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4665703); return false;">Nagiros</a></span>，现在建了<strong><a class="newpage" href="/nagiros">一个作者页</a></strong>.</p>
